# Scene

A scene encompasses one or more story events. Scenes are also where prose is edited.

### Typical properties of a scene include:

- Name
- Summary
- Characters (optional)
- Location
- Scene List 
- Story Events
- Time Unit at which is happens and endures

### Things that can be done or to scene:

- Add or remove scenes
- Add or remove story events
- Name or rename
- Edit prose
- Insert a new scene before or after in the Scene List
- Track characters
- Track locations
- Track symbols
